19 — Minimal next steps (what I recommend you do right now)

Run a 1-week discovery workshop with 5 stakeholders and produce a one-page PRD and 6-month roadmap.

Pick 1 or 2 prioritized use-cases for MVP (e.g., EHR + CHW offline app + one ML screening).

Spin up a small technical spike: a Streamlit/React prototype for the clinical workflow + one simple ML demo on sample data.

Recruit a clinical partner (hospital / public health dept) for pilot site.

